as intending to sell at a profit and handed it out to friends who could use it, and just held on to a couple of things to recoup some of my costs.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Moridam on Remora<br />Rank 6 Bastok<br /><br />http://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?32031<br /><br />As of 5/3: MNK 56/ WAR 29/THF 17/BRD 17/WHM 9 /RNG 5/BST 3<br />AF 1: O 2: O 3: O 4: X 5: X 6: X<br />LB 1: O 2: O 3: X 4: X 5: X</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from Worcester, MA</td></tr></table>
